# Production Environment Variables
# ⚠️ DO NOT EDIT THIS FILE - All values MUST be set in Vercel Dashboard
# Settings → Environment Variables

# These are placeholders - actual values must be configured in Vercel
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://... (required - set in Vercel)
# DIRECT_URL=postgresql://... (required - set in Vercel)
# NEXTAUTH_SECRET=... (required - set in Vercel)
# NEXTAUTH_URL=https://yourdomain.com (required - set in Vercel)
